---
// Footer matching Stitch design exactly
---

<footer class="w-full pt-24 pb-12 border-t border-[#3b494c]/10 bg-[#0a0f13]">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="text-xl font-bold text-[#fff9ef] font-display">BitGuru</div>
      <p class="font-body text-xs leading-relaxed text-[#dfe3e9]/60">
        Elevating your trading skills through professional education and institutional-grade tools.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h4 class="text-on-surface font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">Resources</h4>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <a class="font-body text-xs leading-relaxed text-[#dfe3e9]/60 hover:text-[#00E5FF] transition-transform hover:translate-y-[-2px]" href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>
        <a class="font-body text-xs leading-relaxed text-[#dfe3e9]/60 hover:text-[#00E5FF] transition-transform hover:translate-y-[-2px]" href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h4 class="text-on-surface font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">Support</h4>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <a class="font-body text-xs leading-relaxed text-[#dfe3e9]/60 hover:text-[#00E5FF] transition-transform hover:translate-y-[-2px]" href="/risk-disclosure">Risk Disclosure</a>
        <a class="font-body text-xs leading-relaxed text-[#dfe3e9]/60 hover:text-[#00E5FF] transition-transform hover:translate-y-[-2px]" href="/contact">Contact Support</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <h4 class="text-on-surface font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">Disclaimer</h4>
      <p class="font-body text-xs leading-relaxed text-[#dfe3e9]/60">
        &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} BitGuru. Master the Ledger. Crypto trading involves significant risk. Technical education only.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
